Package edu.uga.dawgtrades.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Attribute
    This interface represents an Attribute describing an Item.
    AttributeType
    This interface represents an AttributeType describing a Category.
    Auction
    This interface represents an Auction of an Item.
    Bid
    This interface represents a Bid placed by a RegisteredUser on an Auction.
    Category
    This interface represents a Category.
    ExperienceReport
    This interface represents an ExperienceReport filed by a RegisteredUser (reviewer) on a different RegisteredUser (reviewed).
    Item
    This interface represents an Item of some Category and owner by a RegisteredUser.
    Membership
    This interface represents a Membership in DawgTrades.
    ObjectModel
    This is the interface to the Object Model subsystem.
    Persistable
    This interface represents the root interface implemented by all entity classes.
    RegisteredUser
    This interface represents a RegisteredUser of DawgTrades.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DTException
    This class represents a DTException, a general exception within the DawgTrades system.
